Web Scraper XML
A high-performance utility designed to extract structured data from web sources
and transform it into standardized XML format.

This tool is built for researchers and analysts who require clean, hierarchical data 
for downstream processing, OSINT investigations, or data protection audits. 
It simplifies the transition from unstructured HTML to machine-readable XML.
